sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as AI Application Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Caikit Chunker<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/4318

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Unary Text Content Detection (/api/v2/text/detection/content)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Header passthrough (Bearer token)
    activate Orch
    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span start (W3C traceparent)

    Orch->>Chunker: tokenization_task_predict (gRPC)<br/>Client certs auth
    activate Chunker
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text tokens
    deactivate Chunker

    par Concurrent detector requests (buffer_unordered)
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token + detector-id header
        activate Detector
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (HAP/PII/etc.)
        deactivate Detector
    end

    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span end + metrics
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with detections
    deactivate Orch

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (/api/v2/chat/completions-detection)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Header passthrough
    activate Orch
    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span start (W3C traceparent)

    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer token (api_token)
    activate OpenAI
    OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response (or SSE stream)
    deactivate OpenAI

    Orch->>Chunker: tokenization (gRPC)<br/>Client certs
    activate Chunker
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked tokens
    deactivate Chunker

    par Concurrent detector requests
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>or /chat or /generation
        activate Detector
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
        deactivate Detector
    end

    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span end + metrics
    Orch-->>Client: SSE stream or JSON with detections
    deactivate Orch

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Classification with Text Generation (v1 Legacy)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Header passthrough
    activate Orch
    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span start (W3C traceparent)

    Orch->>TGIS: generate (gRPC)<br/>Client certs auth
    activate TGIS
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    deactivate TGIS

    Orch->>Chunker: tokenization (gRPC)<br/>Client certs
    activate Chunker
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked tokens
    deactivate Chunker

    par Concurrent detector requests
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token + detector-id
        activate Detector
        Detector-->>Orch: Classification results
        deactivate Detector
    end

    Orch->>OTLP: Trace span end + metrics
    Orch-->>Client: JSON with classification + generated text
    deactivate Orch

    Note over Client,Health: Health Check Flow

    Client->>Health: GET /health (8034/TCP, plaintext)
    activate Health
    Health->>TGIS: gRPC Health.check()
    Health->>Chunker: gRPC Health.check()
    Health->>Detector: HTTP GET /health
    Health->>OpenAI: HTTP GET /health
    Health-->>Client: Aggregated health status
    deactivate Health
